This directory contains static assets for the SCAS Admissions System.

Required assets:
- logo.svg (SCAS logo)
- hero-bg.jpg (Hero background image)
- program-stem.jpg (STEM program image)
- program-bsit.jpg (BSIT program image)
- program-bsba.jpg (BSBA program image)
- program-baed.jpg (BAED program image)
- program-mba.jpg (MBA program image)
- program-abm.jpg (ABM program image)
- pattern.svg (Background pattern)
- favicon.ico (Favicon)

Images should be optimized for web:
- JPEG format for photographs (quality: 80-90%)
- SVG format for logos and icons
- WebP format for modern browsers (optional)
- Maximum width: 1920px for hero images
- File size: Under 500KB per image
